---
/**
 * The Shift / Philosophy Section
 * Value Added Selling: Present the new way of thinking.
 * 3-column layout with the core pillars.
 */
---

<section class="relative w-full py-32 border-t border-white/5">
    <!-- Aurora Background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-[-10%] w-[40%] h-[50%] bg-primary/10 blur-[150px] rounded-full"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-[-10%] w-[30%] h-[40%] bg-blue-900/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-8xl mx-auto px-5vw relative z-10">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
            <span class="font-sans font-semibold text-secondary text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 block">
                The Shift
            </span>
            <h2 class="font-serif font-bold text-white text-4xl lg:text-6xl tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
                Move from <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary to-white">"Hope-Based"</span><br/>
                to <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-secondary">"Deterministic"</span>.
            </h2>
        </div>

        <!-- 3 Pillars Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
            <!-- Pillar 1: Asset First -->
            <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 hover:border-secondary/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(200,169,126,0.1)]">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-secondary/10 border border-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M21 16V8a2 2 0 0 0-1-1.73l-7-4a2 2 0 0 0-2 0l-7 4A2 2 0 0 0 3 8v8a2 2 0 0 0 1 1.73l7 4a2 2 0 0 0 2 0l7-4A2 2 0 0 0 21 16z"></path>
                        <path d="m3.27 6.96 8.73 5.04m0 0 8.73-5.04M12 12v9.5"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Asset First</h3>
                <p class="text-secondary font-medium text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Truth over Documentation.</p>
                <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                    We don't ask people "Did you do X?". We query the infrastructure to prove it. If it's not in the code, it doesn't exist.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Pillar 2: Engineering Resilience -->
            <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 hover:border-secondary/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(200,169,126,0.1)]">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-secondary/10 border border-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10"></path>
                        <path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Engineering Resilience</h3>
                <p class="text-secondary font-medium text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Systems over Willpower.</p>
                <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Policies fail when people get tired. Automated pipelines don't. We build security that works even when everyone is asleep.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Pillar 3: Value Driven GRC -->
            <div class="group relative p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 hover:border-secondary/30 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(200,169,126,0.1)]">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-secondary/10 border border-secondary/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M3 3v18h18"></path>
                        <path d="m19 9-5 5-4-4-3 3"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Value Driven GRC</h3>
                <p class="text-secondary font-medium text-sm uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Competitive Edge over Cost Center.</p>
                <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
                    Stop treating compliance as a tax. Use it to build a cleaner, faster, and more reliable infrastructure.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
